# Cross-compiled Linux hako binaries embedded in the Win/Mac wrappers
# via `cargo build --features embedded`. Produced by:
#
#   cargo xtask build-linux           # x86_64-unknown-linux-musl → hako-linux-x64
#   cargo xtask build-linux --arm64   # aarch64-unknown-linux-musl → hako-linux-arm64
#
# Not committed because they're large (~10MB) and platform-specific.
# CI populates them as part of release builds.
hako-linux-*

# Stub files build.rs creates so include_bytes! always succeeds even
# when no real binary has been cross-compiled yet. Recognized at
# runtime by their tiny size + sentinel bytes.
hako-linux-*.stub
